<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="06af4131-f95c-4d1b-ae38-92cc4f2e7523" >

    <ul> 
 <li>Nominees must be full-time tenure and tenure-track faculty members in the Faculty of Community Services. This includes academic chairs, directors and associate deans</li> 
 <li>Nominees must have at least three years of experience within the Faculty of Community Services</li> 
 <li>Individuals who have received the award within the last five years are not eligible for nomination</li> 
</ul>
    





