<div class="res-text richtextContent background-hidden" id="eebd2f98-9003-4d21-b18c-f2f7999c9371" >

    <p>A completed nomination package includes:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li><p>A <strong>nomination brief</strong> (750 words) which clearly outlines the nominee’s excellence in two of the following areas:</p> 
  <ul> 
   <li><p>Administration</p> </li> 
   <li><p>SRC</p> </li> 
   <li><p>Teaching</p> </li> 
   <li><p>Service</p> </li> 
  </ul> </li> 
 <li><p>A <strong>citation brief</strong> (max 150 words) suitable for public release</p> </li> 
 <li><p>Two <strong>letters of support</strong></p> 
  <ul> 
   <li><p>Each letter should address one of the two areas of excellence</p> </li> 
   <li><p>One letter must be from a faculty member in the Faculty of Community Services</p> </li> 
  </ul> </li> 
</ul> 
<p>If candidate is being nominated for their teaching excellence, we will accept up to two additional letters from students</p>
    





